OL,3,CWales is set to become a Bluetongue
OL,4,CRestricted Zone
OL,6,FWales will become a Bluetongue
OL,7,FRestricted Zone from November 10,
OL,8,FWelsh Government has announced.
OL,10,FThe move will replace the existing
OL,11,FTemporary Control Zone with a single
OL,12,Fnational approach. The decision, which
OL,13,Ftakes into account dropping
OL,14,Ftemperatures and reduced midge
OL,15,Factivity, is designed to simplify
OL,16,Fdisease control measures and support
OL,17,Fongoing surveillance and vaccination
OL,18,Fefforts.
