OL,6,FNFU Cymru has welcomed the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment's announcement. President
OL,8,FAled Jones said: "The move to a whole
OL,9,Fcountry RZ is something NFU Cymru has
OL,10,Fbeen calling for and at the roundtable
OL,11,Fwe expressed our strong support for
OL,12,Fthis way forward. With temperatures
OL,13,Fdropping it is right to move to this
OL,14,Fapproach, all along we have said the
OL,15,Frisks of the disease must be balanced
OL,16,Fagainst the economic and practical
OL,17,Fcosts of the controls.
