OL,6,F"With further cases of BTV-3 confirmed
OL,7,Fin Wales we urge all livestock keepers
OL,8,Fto remain vigilant and to report any
OL,9,Fsuspicion of disease to APHA
OL,10,Fimmediately on 0300 3038268. We
OL,11,Fbelieve that vaccination represents
OL,12,Fthe best way of protecting our flocks
OL,13,Fand herds in Wales and we continue to
OL,14,Frecommend that farmers discuss the
OL,15,Fpotential benefits with their private
OL,16,Fvet to decide if it is right for them."
