OL,3,CWales is set to become a Bluetongue
OL,4,CRestricted Zone
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says its
OL,7,FBluetongue control policy, supported
OL,8,Fby regular evidence-based updates, has
OL,9,Fdelayed Bluetongue incursion from the
OL,10,Fall-England Restricted Zone until the
OL,11,Ftime of year when the impact and
OL,12,Fspread of the disease is limited. It
OL,13,Fhas also provided farmers with
OL,14,Fessential time to vaccinate their
OL,15,Flivestock and prepare for the
OL,16,Femergence of the disease in Wales.
OL,18,FAnimal keepers continue to be
OL,19,Fencouraged to speak to their vets
OL,20,Fabout BTV-3 vaccination to protect
OL,21,Flivestock and livelihoods.
