OL,11,FDeputy First Minister Huw Irranca-
OL,12,FDavies said: "The success of our
OL,13,Fpolicy to date is attributable to the
OL,14,Fhard work of delivery partners
OL,15,Fincluding the Animal and Plant Health
OL,16,FAgency (APHA) and The Pirbright
OL,17,FInstitute, as well as the co-operation
OL,18,Fand goodwill of the livestock sector.
