OL,6,F"I appreciate the restrictions on
OL,7,Flivestock movements and the
OL,8,Fintroduction of the Temporary Control
OL,9,FZone (TCZ), have been disruptive for
OL,10,Flivestock keepers and wider industry.
OL,11,FI have met with the livestock and
OL,12,Fveterinary sectors regularly, in
OL,13,Froundtable meetings, and listened to
OL,14,Ffeedback on the challenges posed by
OL,15,Fboth the restrictions on livestock
OL,16,Fmovements between England and Wales
OL,17,Fand the potential animal health and
OL,18,Fwelfare impacts of Bluetongue.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
