OL,6,F"Following those discussions, and in
OL,7,Fline with my commitment to review our
OL,8,Fposition based on new and emerging
OL,9,Fevidence, I have considered our
OL,10,Fapproach to Bluetongue policy in Wales
OL,11,Ffor the remainder of 2025 and beyond.
OL,13,F"Given that Bluetongue has reached
OL,14,FWales, and historic temperature data
OL,15,Fand modelling work indicates it is
OL,16,Fvery unlikely for midge-borne
OL,17,Ftransmission of Bluetongue virus to
OL,18,Foccur after 10 November in Wales, the
OL,19,Fdeclaration of an all-Wales Restricted
OL,20,FZone will commence on that date."
