OL,6,FWales' Chief Veterinary Officer,
OL,7,FRichard Irvine, urges animal keepers
OL,8,Fto source stock responsibly, remain
OL,9,Fvigilant for the signs of Bluetongue,
OL,10,Fand to report any suspect cases to the
OL,11,FAPHA immediately.
